@startuml ai_worker_pipeline_sequence
!theme cerulean
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title 8-Phase Pipeline Sequence

actor "RobustProcessor" as RP #4A90D9
participant "ContentProcessor\npipeline/" as CP #F5A623
participant "scene/analyzer" as ANA #7ED321
participant "script/chunker" as CHK #F8E71C
participant "scene/validator" as VAL #7ED321
participant "SceneDirector\nscene/director" as SD #7ED321
participant "GPUManager\ncore/" as GPU #95A5A6
participant "fish_client\ntts/" as TTS #9B59B6
participant "PromptEngine\nvideo/" as PE #E74C3C
participant "VideoManager\nvideo/" as VM #E74C3C
participant "LayoutRenderer\nrenderer/" as LR #3498DB

== 1막: LLM (qwen2.5:14b ~14GB) ==

RP -> CP : process_content(content)
activate CP

CP -> ANA : Phase 1: analyze_resources()
activate ANA
return ResourceProfile

CP -> CHK : Phase 2: chunk_with_llm(content, profile)
activate CHK
CHK -> CHK : Ollama LLM 호출
return raw script dict

CP -> VAL : Phase 3: validate_and_fix(script)
activate VAL
return validated script

CP -> SD : Phase 4: distribute(script_data)
activate SD
SD -> SD : 씬 배분 + 감정 태그
return list[SceneDecision]

== VRAM 전환: LLM 해제 ==

CP -> GPU : cleanup(LLM)
activate GPU
GPU -> GPU : torch.cuda.empty_cache()\ngc.collect()
return OK

== 2막: Media (Fish ~5GB + LTX ~12.7GB) ==

CP -> SD : Phase 4.5: assign_video_modes(scenes)
activate SD
SD -> SD : t2v/i2v 결정
return scenes (video_mode set)

CP -> TTS : Phase 5: synthesize(scenes)
activate TTS
TTS -> TTS : Fish Speech TTS
return scene.text_lines + audio

CP -> PE : Phase 6: generate_prompt(scenes)
activate PE
PE -> PE : 한→영 변환 (Ollama)
return scene.video_prompt

CP -> VM : Phase 7: generate_clips(scenes)
activate VM
VM -> VM : ComfyUI LTX-2\n4단계 폴백 재시도
return scene.video_clip_path

CP -> LR : Phase 8: render(scenes)
activate LR
LR -> LR : FFmpeg h264_nvenc\n9:16 합성 + 자막 + 썸네일
return final_video_path

return ScriptData

@enduml
